## Tailwind Class Violations

### Issue: Long Inline Class Chains
Several components have long Tailwind class chains that should be extracted to `globals.css`.

**Affected Components:**
1. **`app-header.tsx`** (line 5):
   - `"w-full flex items-center justify-between rounded-full border border-accent-200/30 bg-white px-10 py-3 shadow-sm"`
   - Should extract to `.header-container` or similar

2. **`app-header.tsx`** (line 13):
   - `"inline-flex items-center justify-center w-8 h-8 rounded-full border border-accent-200/60 bg-white text-background-dark transition hover:border-background-dark hover:bg-accent-900"`
   - Should extract to `.button-icon` or `.icon-button`

3. **`base-panel.tsx`** (line 17):
   - `"h-full rounded-xl border border-accent-200/30 bg-white p-4 shadow-sm"`
   - Should extract to `.card-surface` or `.panel-surface` (reusable pattern)

4. **`upload-feature.tsx`** (line 78):
   - `"h-full rounded-xl border border-accent-200/30 bg-white p-4 shadow-sm"`
   - Same pattern as base-panel - should use shared class

**Recommended Extractions:**
```css
/* Add to globals.css */
.header-container {
  @apply w-full flex items-center justify-between rounded-full border border-accent-200/30 bg-white px-10 py-3 shadow-sm;
}

.icon-button {
  @apply inline-flex items-center justify-center w-8 h-8 rounded-full border border-accent-200/60 bg-white text-background-dark transition hover:border-background-dark hover:bg-accent-900;
}

.card-surface {
  @apply h-full rounded-xl border border-accent-200/30 bg-white p-4 shadow-sm;
}
```

